Listen Innovation Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 25, 2017 9:02 PM ET
Internet Software and Services

Company Overview of Listen Innovation Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Listen Innovation Inc. is an education technology company that provides a listening skills platform, which enables teachers to teach their students to listen with public radio. The company offers Listen Current, a platform that enables teachers to bring authentic voices and engaging non-fiction stories to ELA, social studies, and STEM classrooms, as well as to keep teaching connected to the real world and build student with listening skills. Its platform also enables teachers to create custom online assignments for students, assign listening, and track student progress; and posts daily current events with classroom discussion questions. In addition, the company’s platform provides audio stor...
Listen Innovation Inc. is an education technology company that provides a listening skills platform, which enables teachers to teach their students to listen with public radio. The company offers Listen Current, a platform that enables teachers to bring authentic voices and engaging non-fiction stories to ELA, social studies, and STEM classrooms, as well as to keep teaching connected to the real world and build student with listening skills. Its platform also enables teachers to create custom online assignments for students, assign listening, and track student progress; and posts daily current events with classroom discussion questions. In addition, the company’s platform provides audio stories with lesson plans for middle and high teachers in science, social studies, and ELA that include a listening guide with interactive transcripts, vocabulary, class activities, digital organizers, custom assignments, and additional resources. Further, it offers Listen Current PREMIUM, a solution for blended, BYOD, flipped, and 1:1 classrooms. Listen Innovation Inc. was formerly known as Listen Edition LLC and changed its name to Listen Innovation Inc. in January 2014. The company was founded in 2013 and is based in Brookline, Massachusetts.
Detailed Description


